                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.51/2330a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McGurk</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-09-25T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 25, 1931—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>66. From de la Rue for Pixley. Advise immediately has the detailed budget been
                    officially submitted to our office for study in compliance with the agreement of
                    August 5th.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
